org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor

Class TestPostIncrementAndAppendBeforeWAL

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor.TestPostIncrementAndAppendBeforeWAL

  • public class TestPostIncrementAndAppendBeforeWAL
extends Object
    Test coprocessor methods RegionObserver.postIncrementBeforeWAL(ObserverContext, Mutation, List) and RegionObserver.postAppendBeforeWAL(ObserverContext, Mutation, List). These methods may change the cells which will be applied to memstore and WAL. So add unit test for the case which change the cell's column family.
